      "side": 1,
      "message": "The mock is required because check_alint calls options.tool_path(\"alint\"), which triggers an eager expansion of all placeholders. This process includes evaluating ${REPO_ROOT}, which calls rh.git.find_repo_root().\n\nSince test_alint specifically mocks rh.utils.run to return a CompletedProcess object (which has stdout\u003dNone by default), find_repo_root would otherwise crash when attempting to .strip() that output. This mock prevents the crash and ensures the test remains hermetic by avoiding actual filesystem/git lookups.",
      "parentUuid": "ba135670_11be4ff0",
